"<br>If LISa doesn't find all hosts you could try to decrease this value."
"<br>"
msgstr ""
"Sawl pecyn ping ddylai LISa anfon ar un tro?"
"<br>Os nad yw LISa'n canfod pob gwesteiwr gallech geisio gostwng y werth hon."
"<br>"

#: setupwizard.cpp:326
